title: TEKKEN 8 — Azucena Official New Character Reveal Trailer
description:
Check out Azucena a brand new character coming to Tekken 8. Azucena was revealed today at EVO 2023. Check out the reveal and gameplay!

Not everyone can handle a strong and punchy blend!
Azucena the Peruvian coffee queen will give you a taste of defeat in Tekken 8.
